    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can expect a smooth ride from day one! It shows a little bit of character from regular use, but it\u2019s clean, runs great, and is totally ready for your next adventure. I\u2019ve priced it to sell quickly because I\u2019d love for someone to start enjoying it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
