    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 equipped with the high-revving S54 inline-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example features documented subframe reinforcement and a recently overhauled VANOS system to ensure optimal cam timing and throttle response across the powerband. The chassis is dialed in with refreshed bushings and a variable M differential lock that provides exceptional mechanical grip out of corners. While the exterior shows minor road-going character consistent with its use, the powertrain and suspension geometry remain sharp, delivering the quintessential analog performance these chassis are renowned for.",
